      • clone

        public ConfigurationObjectBase clone()
        When cloning a configuration object we create a deep copy of its attributes but only a shallow copy of the configuration registry used to obtain the child properties elements. As a result, when a configuration object is cloned and while it keeps its configuration name it will have the same child properties elements as the original.
